We're almost there,
so let's run the last leg.

943
00:57:39,363 --> 00:57:41,493
- What?
- Come on. Let's run.

944
00:57:41,774 --> 00:57:44,374
I really wish you'd just say it here.

945
00:57:44,374 --> 00:57:46,163
Come on. Run.

946
00:57:46,544 --> 00:57:49,004
What do you want to say at the peak?

947
00:58:21,113 --> 00:58:22,734
You're still young.

948
00:58:22,914 --> 00:58:25,873
When you get married,
you'll understand how I feel.

949
00:58:25,944 --> 00:58:27,873
The eyes show if you've been in love.

950
00:58:30,584 --> 00:58:32,143
It's not the case for you.

951
00:58:32,453 --> 00:58:35,444
I want you to feel that blissful moment...

952
00:58:37,894 --> 00:58:39,384
once in your life.

953
00:58:45,303 --> 00:58:46,823
Love?

954
00:58:49,703 --> 00:58:50,933
Hey.

955
00:59:19,004 --> 00:59:20,194
My gosh.

956
00:59:24,703 --> 00:59:25,933
Here.

957
00:59:28,044 --> 00:59:29,334
Thank you.

958
00:59:33,883 --> 00:59:35,243
I feel much better.

959
00:59:35,714 --> 00:59:37,643
I have something to tell you.

960
00:59:38,254 --> 00:59:39,444
Go ahead.

961
00:59:39,653 --> 00:59:42,614
Shall we turn on the love system
Dr. Brain mentioned?

962
00:59:44,624 --> 00:59:48,183
You and I should give love a try.

963
00:59:49,194 --> 00:59:50,393
What?

964
